  <brief_title>A Study of Oral Methylnaltrexone (MNTX) for the Treatment of Opioid-Induced Constipation in Subjects With Chronic, Non-Malignant Pain</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 3, Multicenter, Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled, Parallel-group Study of Oral Methylnaltrexone (OM) for the Treatment of Opioid-Induced Constipation (OIC) in Subjects With Chronic, Non-Malignant Pain</official_title>
