  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      MNTX 3201 is a Phase 3, international, multicenter, randomized, double-blind,
      placebo-controlled, parallel-group study in order to evaluate the safety and efficacy of oral
      MNTX for the treatment of opioid induced constipation in subjects with chronic, non-malignant
      pain.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
